{"tid":1890783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"口罩價格較上周下跌三至四成　酒精搓手液貨量增","createTime":"2020-02-21T11:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T08:49:40.000Z","uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d49dcc9b8c3a79f0144d1926633553ede35384ca","tid":1890783,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"口罩價格較上周下跌三至四成 酒精搓手液貨量增<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情下，口罩、酒精搓手液、消毒藥水等防疫用品頓成搶手貨，價格一度被炒高數倍至數十倍。記者上星期走訪銅鑼灣區所有藥房，當時一盒50片的口罩大多介乎$300至$500。本周四（20日）重遊故地，發現所有口罩都有減價的跡象，一盒50片的口罩，最低售價僅$180，比上星期的最低售價$298，下跌接近四成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-20200220215752_1022_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-20200220215752_1022_large.jpg&h=06c19f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者今日巡視銅鑼灣多間藥房的口罩價格。眾新聞製圖<br />\n其中三款來自印尼的不同品牌口罩，包括：Diapro、NEO及IND life，價格均比上周大幅下跌。<br />\n<br />\n牌子 上周價 昨日價 跌幅<br />\nDiapro $430 $300 約30%<br />\nNEO    $460 $298 約35%<br />\nIND life $398 $298 約25%<br />\n<br />\n另外，一款聲稱香港製造及獨立包裝的Healthcare外科口罩，售價為$450，冠絕銅鑼灣。店員表示，這款口罩質量及手工均比其他做得細緻，故售價比較昂貴，但被問到其功效有否比其他牌子口罩優勝時，店員則答「咁又冇咩大分別嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-20200220221217_c198_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-20200220221217_c198_large.jpg&h=ed415523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一款聲稱香港製造及獨立包裝的Healthcare外科口罩，售價為$450，冠絕銅鑼灣。<br />\n網上售賣的防疫用品貨源亦見增加。HK TV mall 的口罩貨量一向緊絀，過往即使是沒有防病毒功效的PITTA防塵防霧霾口罩，上架不久都極速被搶購一空。昨日架上可見口罩款式增加不少，不過價格則未見大幅回落。其中3M Nexcare 外科三層口罩，平均$14至$15一個；韓國KF94口罩，平均26至30元一個；至於一盒50至65個裝的口罩，價格仍然高企，約450元至999元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC-20200220221206_5633_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B3%25BC-20200220221206_5633_large.jpg&h=e7d8620a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHK TV mall 的口罩（左）及酒精搓手液（右）不少仍然有貨。網上截圖<br />\n至於不少港人光顧的Amazon亞馬遜日本網站，記者1月31日瀏覽各款口罩售價，其中3M N95口罩，一盒50個訂價96,999日元（約6,943港元），平均每個1,940日元（約139港元）；昨日最便宜可賣到4,800日元（約334港元），平均每個96日元（約7港元）。相隔20日，價格是之前的1/20。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-20200220223025_2ee8_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-20200220223025_2ee8_large.jpg&h=e67d281a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在Amazon亞馬遜日本網站，一盒50個3M N95口罩，上月31日賣96,999日元（約6,943港元）（上圖）；今日最便宜的貨源賣4,800日元（約334港元）（下圖）。<br />\n不過，另一款一盒有30個的フィッティ 7DAYS外科口罩，1月31日售價為5,200日元（約373港元），即平均每個173日元（約12.4港元）。昨日所見售價為3包15,500日元，即每包5,167日元 （約359港元），即平均每個172日元（約12港元），變化不大。<br />\n<br />\n另外，酒精搓手液、消毒藥水等搶手貨，貨源亦見增加。除了大型連鎖集團陸續售貨外，記者在銅鑼灣一帶藥房亦見有大量不同牌子的消毒用品，當中包括滴露及威露士等大牌子。HK TV mall亦見有大量酒精搓手液出售，不過售價亦同樣未有顯著下跌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81-20200220224713_1906_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581-20200220224713_1906_large.jpg&h=75e87695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅鑼灣藥房門外擺賣大量消毒用品。<br />\n早前人人搶購各種消毒用品，網上拍賣平台亦有不少貨源，惟部分售價較平常高數倍。以滴露1.8L裝消毒藥水為例，在網上拍賣平台Carousel，一星期前有人賣到300元。今天在HK tv mall上架滴露官方店及百佳網店仍然缺貨，不過記者見到有藥房以$95出售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81-20200220224616_2ed2_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581-20200220224616_2ed2_large.jpg&h=f51036d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滴露1.8L裝消毒藥水，一星期前在網上拍賣平台Carousel有人賣$300（左）；1月底有網民發現有藥房賣$200（中）。昨天有藥房賣$95（右）。<br />\n而較為罕見的滴露濕紙巾，藥房昨日賣13元一包；但一星期前在Carousel，有人以55元一包發售，貴3倍多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81-20200220224609_1d36_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581-20200220224609_1d36_large.jpg&h=222e357d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滴露濕紙巾有人一星期前在Carousel賣$55（左），今日藥房賣$13（右）。<br />\n威露士免洗酒精搓手液250ml裝，百佳網店原價為$29.9，一星期前在Carousel有人賣$250，而記者昨日在藥房所見則售$50。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81-20200220224602_1dd5_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581-20200220224602_1dd5_large.jpg&h=e12060a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n威露士免洗酒精搓手液一星期前在Carousel有人賣$250（左），今日有藥房售$50（右）。"},{"pid":"99b92395aa7445b6fcc1e0605be63cad181dc247","tid":1890783,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca4016accd3ae1da6c6e146f410b8f1c152821a","tid":1890783,"uid":101242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:26:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾罩都賣300<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab994533a3567a9fa2830fbcd0be6053398444dc","tid":1890783,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"見到NEO罩賣180 無人買"},{"pid":"3339f1a297312249d379837d887965fdad522db2","tid":1890783,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"免費野~~比一蚊都兼多, 去龍津買野食食左D錢好D"},{"pid":"7c0bb9a9b87b185774cc8adba146dbabfb662385","tid":1890783,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"df014577c0ccf2b0bb75fbb1c89a7a024ef1ce8a","tid":1890783,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"250免洗手液<br />\n傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bc6feb5b9f0373c0a5ae2f544a3817d9bf172d","tid":1890783,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"貴唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係用黎買印尼罩姐<br />\n<br />\n有astm EN14683嗰啲貴一貴都有人買<br />\n<br />\n始終條命緊要d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96b226f8d24232898879df1df9ad78af4421e05","tid":1890783,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"三四月難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28729d300d5edf007146be5e2d79c536d4b2871c","tid":1890783,"uid":81045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾印尼罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e97edaca05e49371de87f889cb2264a887d1855","tid":1890783,"uid":39911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"日本罩依然需求大"},{"pid":"b485a93d136ee61e6f9b9919a08f4e79f68e6f28","tid":1890783,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96b226f8d24232898879df1df9ad78af4421e05","tid":1890783,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0